{
  "category": "greetings",
  "templates": [
    {
      "id": "social_rich_001",
      "text": "Hail, {player}! Fernalla's blessings upon you this fine day.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_002",
      "text": "Well met, {player}. May Brax's flame light your way through the dark places.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_003",
      "text": "Another brave soul from Stowaway's Step! Good to see new faces in Port Azure.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "zone"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_004",
      "text": "Hail, {player}. Vitheo's winds must have carried you here for a reason.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Vitheo's Watch"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_005",
      "text": "Welcome, friend. The Torchbearers of Brax say any who walk by the Lighthouse flame walk in truth.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_006",
      "text": "Good day, {player}. Soluna's light still touches this land, despite everything.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Soluna's Landing"],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_007",
      "text": "Greetings from Fernalla's Revival Plains, {player}. The great willow still stands. That must count for something.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore", "zone"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fernalla's Revival Plains"],
      "personality_affinity": ["warm", "scholarly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_008",
      "text": "Ah, {player}! I thought I was alone out here. Careful around these parts, the Sivakayans have been sighted again.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Silkengrass Meadowlands", "Blacksalt Strand"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_009",
      "text": "Brax built this world with love, and here we stand in it. Good to see you, {player}.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_010",
      "text": "Hello, {player}. You have the look of someone who has walked the Braxonian Desert and lived. Respect.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "zone"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Braxonian Desert"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_011",
      "text": "Hail, wanderer. The Blades of Vitheo welcome all who fight with honor.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_012",
      "text": "Glad to see a friendly face, {player}. The Wisp's wards keep Loomingwood safe, but the rest of this continent is another story.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Loomingwood"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "scholarly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_013",
      "text": "Welcome, {player}. I hope you carry better news than the last traveler from Duskenlight Coast.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "zone"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Duskenlight Coast"],
      "personality_affinity": ["neutral", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_014",
      "text": "Greetings, {player}. By Fernalla's grace, the land still blooms. Even here.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fernalla's Revival Plains"],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_015",
      "text": "Another warrior of The Azure Guard! Well met, {player}. Captain Kilkay has us all on edge, but the walls hold.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_016",
      "text": "Fernalla watch over you, {player}. Safe travels out there.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_017",
      "text": "May Vitheo's winds carry you safe. Watch for storms near Duskenlight Coast.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Duskenlight Coast"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_018",
      "text": "Walk carefully, {player}. Brax turned his back on us, but his fire still burns at the Lighthouse. Find your way by it.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_019",
      "text": "Until we meet again, {player}. The Solunarian Brotherhood teaches that each parting is just a turn in the road.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_020",
      "text": "Stay sharp out there. The Children of Sivakaya do not rest, and neither should we. Go well, {player}.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["neutral", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_021",
      "text": "Go with Brax's strength, {player}. Tread carefully if you head north of Silkengrass Meadowlands.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Silkengrass Meadowlands"],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_022",
      "text": "Farewell, {player}. If the Wisp's teachings hold true, then Siva is not lost forever. Hold onto that.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Loomingwood"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 3.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_023",
      "text": "Take care, friend. Even Fernalla's children know that death is part of the cycle. Just make sure it is not yours today.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_024",
      "text": "Keep your blade close and Soluna's light closer, {player}. The night belongs to darker things.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "lore", "blessing"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_025",
      "text": "Safe roads, {player}. Avoid The Blight if you can. That land drinks the life right out of you.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "farewell", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_026",
      "text": "Something feels different about Loomingwood lately. Darker, heavier. The wards are holding, but just barely.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Loomingwood"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_027",
      "text": "The sand never stops blowing in the Braxonian Desert. Brax buried everything he loved under it. You can feel the grief in every gust.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Braxonian Desert"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_028",
      "text": "Have you stood at Soluna's Landing at dusk? The crater still glows. Stars that fell centuries ago, still burning.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Soluna's Landing"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_029",
      "text": "The air in Rottenfoot stinks of marsh gas and old blood. I have never understood why anyone camps there willingly.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rottenfoot"],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_030",
      "text": "Faerie's Brake is beautiful, but never let your guard down. The faeries do not care whether you find them charming.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Faerie's Brake"],
      "personality_affinity": ["neutral", "playful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_031",
      "text": "The sea wind off Blacksalt Strand carries salt and something else. Some say it is Vitheo weeping for his mother.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Blacksalt Strand"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_032",
      "text": "Windwashed Pass is the kind of place where the mountains watch you. The Stonemen used to be scholars, you know. Now they just stand there.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Windwashed Pass"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_033",
      "text": "There is a stillness in Fernalla's Revival Plains that nowhere else in Erenshor has. Like the land remembers her.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fernalla's Revival Plains"],
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_034",
      "text": "The Blight crawls eastward every year. You can see where Fernalla's power pushes back, but the line keeps shifting.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_035",
      "text": "Hidden Hills is quiet today. Good. Last time I passed through, the Priel bandits had camps on every ridge.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "zone", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Hidden Hills"],
      "personality_affinity": ["neutral", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_036",
      "text": "I was speaking with Cerbantias Flameward at the Lighthouse. He says the flame has never flickered. Not once since Brax lit it.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_037",
      "text": "Fernalla's Children are still searching for the Great Willow's Branch. Orion Mycon believes it is the key to healing these lands.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "devout"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_038",
      "text": "The Solunarian Brotherhood keeps the faith in Port Azure, but I wonder sometimes. Soluna left us too, just like Brax.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_039",
      "text": "Captain Kilkay closed the ports and pulled the guard behind the walls. Ripper DeMerth refused. Honestly? I think Ripper had it right.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["neutral", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_040",
      "text": "I traded some Ogrespice Leaf with a druid from Fernalla's Children yesterday. They swear it cures more than just hunger.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_041",
      "text": "Grayleigh Hawke of The Blades of Vitheo says the sea speaks to those who listen. I have tried. All I hear are waves.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_042",
      "text": "The Agents of The Wisp in Loomingwood have blue-tinged skin. Comes from living too close to the Nighthollow Candle. Strange folk, but they mean well.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Loomingwood"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_043",
      "text": "The Torchbearers of Brax at the Lighthouse help Arcanists with their studies. If you are one, pay them a visit.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "scholarly"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_044",
      "text": "Eldoth Molorai claims they are protecting Erenshor. They have a funny way of showing it, attacking anyone who sets foot near Old Krakengard.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Old Krakengard", "Azynthi's Garden"],
      "personality_affinity": ["neutral", "playful"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_045",
      "text": "Savannah Priel tried to tame Malaroths and ship them to Merosavilla. That woman has more nerve than sense. Respect it, though.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "faction", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Malaroth's Nesting Grounds", "Prielian Cascade"],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_046",
      "text": "You believe in the old gods? I think Soluna had the right idea. Just leave. This continent is more trouble than it is worth.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "lore", "zone"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_047",
      "text": "I asked Braxon Nelmar what happened to Brax. He just stared at the Lighthouse flame and said nothing. Real uplifting, that.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Port Azure"],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "friendly"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_048",
      "text": "The Stonemen at Rockshade Hold scratched Azynthi's name into their walls. They cannot speak, cannot write, but they managed that. Makes you wonder.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "lore", "zone"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Rockshade Hold"],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_049",
      "text": "A druid told me that Fernalla embraces death as part of nature's cycle. I said I would rather not be embraced just yet, thank you.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "lore", "faction"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["playful", "warm"],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    },
    {
      "id": "social_rich_050",
      "text": "Siva and Brax created this world out of love. Then a single student ruined it all. Sometimes I think Azynthi was the most dangerous thing to ever walk Amarion.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "lore"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": ["scholarly", "neutral"],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.0,
      "sim_name": null
    }
  ]
}
